Katya: I agree. He seemed deceptive and honorless. If all his unit is 
the same.

Blackfang shook his head.

Blackfang: Not so sure about that. From what I know, and I can say I 
know quite a lot on these guys, their commander is a direct descendant 
of Optimus Prime and a relative of Talos. From what I heard, he's 
quite fond of pred-busting and very direct too, but I guess he's okay. 
And even though I hate their ways, they are VERY efficient. They 
prevented that terrorist act on the capital 2 mega-cycles ago and they 
managed to end the hostage taking of Ujika with minimal casualties. 
They are strong. And I think that if one has turned pred, he should be 
one of the primary targets.
